title: Cool Savory Muffins - Alex Kuskowski
description: What easy-to-cook food can be served as dessert, snacks, dinner, lunch, or even breakfast? Muffins of course! Kids will love trying their hand at baking one of the most versatile and tasty foods. Get ready to whip up some family classics. Cool Savory Muffins are fun to make and easy to eat. Try Mac & Cheesy Bites or Super Savory Herb Pops. Muffins make a great snack any time of day. Includes full-page spreads on ingredients and tools to help make baking easy!
